cellml_events Namespace Reference


Classes

interface  MutationEvent

Detailed Description

The CellML Events module is an optional extension which may be supported by implementations of the CellML API. It provides a mechanism by which applications can be informed of changes to the CellML model.

It is built on top of W3C DOM Level 2 events model.
